###
### Gửi yêu cầu tạo event mới
### Gửi yêu cầu tạo event mới (Dạng Form Data)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary_12345

--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

React Summit 2026
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Google's premier cloud computing event...
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="overview"

React 2025 highlights...
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="event2.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< public\images\event2.png
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="venue"

Amsterdam Center
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="location"

Amsterdam, Netherlands
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="date"

2026-04-20
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="time"

10:30
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="mode"

hybrid
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audience"

Cloud engineers, DevOps, enterprise leaders, AI researchers
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="agenda"

08:30 AM - 09:30 AM | Keynote: AI-Driven Cloud Infrastructure
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="organizer"

Google Cloud
--boundary_12345
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tags"

Cloud, DevOps, Kubernetes, AI
--boundary_12345--

### Fetch all events from MongoDB
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events
Accept: application/json

### Fetch a single event by ID (example)
# GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/YOUR_EVENT_ID_HERE